}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b\f1 70-75.}{\plain \fs24 \f1   See Daniel J. Donno, "Dante's Ulysses and Virgil's Prohibition," }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 Italica}{\plain \fs24 \f1  50 (1973), \softline
